妥協，以換小命。如今法案雖獲很多美國議員支持，值得高興，卻不能掉以輕心。確保法案能有效威脅中共，才能幫助香港。絕不減辣，我要攬炒！（我抄 香港自治行動 專頁嘅）<br />\n<br />\n留意返，呢個聯署一定要快達標，因為要盡早畀美國國會知道我哋嘅意願。<br />\n<br />\n簽＞查電郵＞確認電郵＞叫十個人簽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsi0CXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxsi0CXD.jpg&h=07f787be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b89bdd2d99ef45421b5fa18567ca286c3bf9030d","tid":1578544,"uid":229923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfe3a360b1de0185e4894b38ac2813b43ca7296","tid":1578544,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5992d0b2b5284d55b216852d0f9f73f272b0dfc","tid":1578544,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:25:01.000Z","msg":"連b我俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />help"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"而家個名最啱你啦"},{"pid":"aa5702ba7e5f7d956b4014001a149b1141992a0a","tid":1578544,"uid":73518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f4fb3cd1f8596dbf356971e2e0a0d46704cefe5","tid":1578544,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f0d9c71cf7ad468aa98e68ba79e5144b72b854a","tid":1578544,"uid":206337,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kATPwpP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkATPwpP.gif&h=6941dbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /